  "title": "Добавить regression для duplicate `fullName` в manual API profile",
  "description": "## T-0993 [ ] P3: Добавить regression для duplicate `fullName` в manual API profile\n\n- Создана: 2026-07-08T18:11:00+03:00\n- Состояние: open\n- Приоритет: P3\n- Execution class: `internal-substrate`\n- Scheduling tier: `later`\n- Зависимости: T-0990\n- Ссылки:\n  - Доменный документ: `docs/documentation/api-manifest.md`\n  - Исходный код: `eng/Electron2D.Build/RepositoryPolicyVerifiers.cs`\n  - Тесты: `tests/Electron2D.Tests.Integration/RepositoryBuildToolTests.cs`\n  - Источник follow-up: `docs/verdicts/release-management/t-0990-audit-r05.md`\n\n### Execution contract\n\n- Task type: test-hardening\n- Ready-to-start:\n  - task state is `open`.\n  - duplicate `fullName` rejection remains implemented in manual profile reader.\n  - a focused RED test can duplicate a profile `fullName` in an API compatibility fixture.\n- Stop conditions:\n  - the change would alter manual profile approval semantics instead of adding coverage.\n  - the test would depend on generated Wiki text instead of profile validation.\n- May change:\n  - focused integration tests for manual profile validation.\n  - profile verifier diagnostics only if the test reveals an actual gap.\n  - task notes and diary for this task.\n- Must not change:\n  - runtime public API implementation.\n  - approved/deferred/unsupported profile decisions.\n  - saved audit reports.\n- Required outputs:\n  - focused regression for diagnostic `E2D-BUILD-API-PROFILE-DUPLICATE-TYPE`.\n- Required commands:\n  - targeted duplicate-profile test.\n  - `dotnet run --project eng/Electron2D.Build -- verify audit-followups`\n  - `git diff --check`\n- External audit:\n  - not required unless bundled with a parent API tooling package.\n\n### Самодостаточное описание\n\nr05 primary audit for `T-0990` found that duplicate `fullName` rejection is implemented in production code, but the focused invalid-profile test set does not include an explicit regression for diagnostic `E2D-BUILD-API-PROFILE-DUPLICATE-TYPE`. This is a test-hardening follow-up, not a current blocker.\n\n### Internal substrate acceptance contract\n\n- Duplicate manual profile rows fail closed with a stable diagnostic.\n- Coverage remains fixture-driven and does not manually approve runtime public API types.\n- The task is limited to validation tests unless the RED test exposes a real implementation gap.\n\n### Критерии приёмки\n\n- [ ] Focused regression creates duplicate `fullName` rows and fails with `E2D-BUILD-API-PROFILE-DUPLICATE-TYPE`.\n- [ ] Existing invalid-profile validation tests remain green.\n- [ ] `verify audit-followups` passes with the closure note from r05.\n\n### Подзадачи\n\n- [ ] Add RED regression for duplicate manual profile `fullName`.\n- [ ] Fix verifier only if the RED test exposes an implementation gap.\n- [ ] Run focused invalid-profile checks, `verify audit-followups` and `git diff --check`.\n\n### Current evidence\n\n- audit-followup-closure:\n  - source: docs/verdicts/release-management/t-0990-audit-r02.md\n  - id: FOLLOW_UP_FINDING F3\n  - state: tracked-new\n  - target: T-0993\n  - rationale: Primary audit r02 classified missing duplicate-`fullName` regression as P3 test hardening. Duplicate rejection is already implemented, so this task tracks focused coverage without expanding current `T-0990` scope.\n- audit-followup-closure:\n  - source: docs/verdicts/release-management/t-0990-audit-r03.md\n  - id: FOLLOW_UP_FINDING F3\n  - state: tracked-new\n  - target: T-0993\n  - rationale: Primary audit r03 repeated the same missing duplicate-`fullName` regression finding. `T-0993` owns focused coverage across all `T-0990` iterations.\n- audit-followup-closure:\n  - source: docs/verdicts/release-management/t-0990-audit-r04.md\n  - id: FOLLOW_UP_FINDING F3\n  - state: tracked-new\n  - target: T-0993\n  - rationale: Primary audit r04 repeated the same missing duplicate-`fullName` regression finding. `T-0993` owns focused coverage across all `T-0990` iterations.\n- audit-followup-closure:\n  - source: docs/verdicts/release-management/t-0990-audit-r05.md\n  - id: FOLLOW_UP_FINDING F3\n  - state: tracked-new\n  - target: T-0993\n  - rationale: Primary audit r05 classified missing duplicate-`fullName` regression as P3 test hardening. Duplicate rejection is already implemented, so this task tracks focused coverage without expanding current `T-0990` scope.\n- audit-followup-closure:\n  - source: docs/verdicts/release-management/t-0990-audit-r06.md\n  - id: FOLLOW_UP_FINDING F3\n  - state: tracked-existing\n  - target: T-0993\n  - rationale: Primary audit r06 repeated the same missing duplicate-`fullName` regression finding and explicitly pointed to existing `T-0993`; no new task is needed.\n- audit-followup-closure:\n  - source: docs/verdicts/release-management/t-0990-audit-r07.md\n  - id: FOLLOW_UP_FINDING F3\n  - state: tracked-existing\n  - target: T-0993\n  - rationale: Accepted primary audit r07 repeated the same missing duplicate-`fullName` regression finding and explicitly pointed to existing `T-0993`; no new task is needed.\n- audit-followup-closure:\n  - source: docs/verdicts/release-management/t-0990-audit-r08.md\n  - id: FOLLOW_UP_FINDING F3\n  - state: tracked-existing\n  - target: T-0993\n  - rationale: Primary audit r08 repeated the same missing duplicate-`fullName` regression finding and explicitly pointed to existing `T-0993`; no new task is needed.\n- audit-followup-closure:\n  - source: docs/verdicts/release-management/t-0990-audit-r09.md\n  - id: FOLLOW_UP_FINDING F3\n  - state: tracked-existing\n  - target: T-0993\n  - rationale: Accepted primary audit r09 repeated the same missing duplicate-`fullName` regression finding and explicitly pointed to existing `T-0993`; no new task is needed.\n- audit-followup-closure:\n  - source: docs/verdicts/release-management/t-0990-audit-r10.md\n  - id: FOLLOW_UP_FINDING F3\n  - state: tracked-existing\n  - target: T-0993\n  - rationale: Accepted primary audit r10 repeated the same missing duplicate-`f